
reassign profile:

https://blog.simos.info/how-to-easily-run-graphics-accelerated-gui-apps-in-lxd-containers-on-your-ubuntu-desktop/

$ lxc profile assign oldcontainer default,gui
$ lxc restart oldcontainer


